&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated successful problem-solving abilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foundational understanding of cybersecurity principles, threats, and best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge of networks, systems, cloud environments, and endpoint security tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Critical thinking and analytical skills to identify and investigate suspicious activity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to follow procedures, document findings, and support incident response activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills and attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize tasks and meet deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to engage professionally across teams and levels of the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
